**Data Attribution Notice:**

This software aggregates data from third-party humanitarian sources including:
- SOS Venezuela 2026 (sosvenezuela2026.com)
- Apoyo Venezuela (apoyovenezuela.com)
- ApoyoVzla (apoyovzla.com)
- Red Solidaria Venezuela (redsolidariavenezuela.com)
- Hospitales en Venezuela (hospitalesenvenezuela.com)

All data remains the property of its respective sources. This project only
normalizes and displays data with proper attribution. No ownership claims are
made over third-party data.
